entity.name: Hurricane Dorian: Category 2 expected to make landfall over eastern Canada early Saturday evening
entity.description: Post-tropical cyclone Dorian, which has already damaged or destroyed thousands of homes in the Bahamas and claimed at least 43 lives, made landfall near Halifax on Saturday evening.

data.text: Our Labor Day Weekend guests have changed their dates. Consequently, we have an unexpected vacancy for any coastal families evacuating from Hurricane Dorian. We have bedding for up to 18 persons and your pets, boats, etc. are always welcome. Contact us at https://t.co/C1C1NNiavt

entity.name: Warning issued for Barbados as Tropical Storm Dorian approaches
entity.description: The National Hurricane Center issued a tropical storm warning for Barbados on Sunday as Tropical Storm Dorian approaches the island. A tropical storm watch is in effect for St. Lucia, St. Vincent and the Grenadines.

entity.name: Tropical Storm Dorian picks up strength as it nears landfall in Puerto Rico
entity.description: Forecasters say Tropical Storm Dorian could reach near-hurricane strength as it makes landfall in Puerto Rico on Wednesday.
